{"root":{"data":{"id":"djvbx91ttbs0","created":1783731156895,"text":"双穿世界","expandState":"expand","font-size":32,"color":"#ff0000"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djvbxm9qab40","created":1783731185671,"text":"梦魇世界","expandState":"expand","layout":null,"font-size":24,"color":"#00b0f0"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djvmk998fxs0","created":1783761170818,"text":"世界信息","layout":null,"font-size":16,"font-weight":"bold"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djvmmssjgeg0","created":1783761370072,"text":"世界信息","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djvmr9hqlrc0","created":1783761719881,"text":"现在是2016年,4年前2012年12月21日世界上有人觉醒了精神异能,但是并不是所有人都能很快发现自己的能力","priority":1,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvndtdbfog0","created":1783763487161,"text":"觉醒精神异能者,能力只与精神力有关,他们被世人称为梦魇","priority":2},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvneh7s3bs0","created":1783763539069,"text":"梦魇使用能力会大量消耗自己的精神力,只能通过睡眠或者吸食高智慧动物精神来恢复精神力","priority":3},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvnmkqt9so0","created":1783764173663,"text":"梦魇不及时恢复能力就会头晕恍惚,甚至休克,严重者会彻底植物人,被摄魂者也会出现这些症状","priority":4},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvno3bz5hs0","created":1783764292489,"text":"摄魂时要么精神力远远强于对方,比如猪牛狗等,要么需要对面处于睡眠休克或者精神崩溃才能摄魂","priority":5},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djvmn9gzfog0","created":1783761406379,"text":"政府结构","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djvnqrvkhsw0","created":1783764502645,"text":"夏国与现世一致的政府架构,也存在联合国等组织","priority":1},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvnsr87kds0","created":1783764657961,"text":"夏国的749局为官方的梦魇组织,其组织目的是控制国内外梦魇力量,维稳国家力量","priority":2},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djvmnn2i4rc0","created":1783761435978,"text":"针对超能力者态度","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djvnvi5shh40","created":1783764873316,"text":"夏国政府一致口径是合作包容,共同繁荣,但是一直忌惮梦魇","priority":1},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvnyhfg0r40","created":1783765106816,"text":"749局是政府控制梦魇的抓手,会将部分梦魇控制并进行研究,749局也被政府忌惮","priority":2},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvnzs14rc00","created":1783765208259,"text":"民间组织\"阴司\"则是想通过组织梦魇来争取平等权利,甚至取代政府,阴司设十殿阎罗,地藏王,孟婆判官等来作为代号,普通成员为拘魂使","priority":3},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djvmi8wc7lk0","created":1783761013309,"text":"李其乐","layout":null,"font-weight":"bold","font-size":16,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djvml701ryo0","created":1783761244273,"text":"家庭信息","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djvms9ddn340","created":1783761797981,"text":"父亲:李雅军,山阳玻璃厂钳工班班长","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvmu75ario0","created":1783761949868,"text":"母亲:郭香兰,山阳玻璃厂流水线打包女工,2015年发现自己觉醒了精神异能","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvmwwx5cyo0","created":1783762162700,"text":"大伯:李雅国,客悦饭馆,拿手菜:酱焖流河草鱼","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvn0l23zt40","created":1783762450335,"text":"堂姐:李其凤,大伯女儿,同省普通一本大学生,临近毕业","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvn1m1ghmg0","created":1783762530836,"text":"堂哥:李其麟,大伯儿子,同一学校同一届高中生","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djvmlx13pvc0","created":1783761300933,"text":"身份背景","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djvn2gj1k1s0","created":1783762597203,"text":"李其乐:山阳县一中高一5班学生,住址:青州大流河西郡山阳县南河湾小区6栋2单元5楼","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvn36vquxk0","created":1783762654568,"text":"堂哥李其麟:山阳县一中高一1班学生,住址:青州大流河西郡山阳县观峰镇通达路客悦饭馆","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djwa812zesg0","created":1783827919293,"text":"学校住址:"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djvmme9ws3k0","created":1783761338472,"text":"行为与性格","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djvn5a2gcdc0","created":1783762818232,"text":"李其乐:漏风嘴,说话不过脑子,自尊心强敏感,学习一般,喜欢玩虐杀原型","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvn87h0o200","created":1783763047675,"text":"李其麟:办事稳重,学习较突出,对比李其乐就是隔壁家孩子","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvnai240680","created":1783763227446,"text":"父亲李雅军:甘于平庸,无不良嗜好"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvnbsvh01c0","created":1783763329353,"text":"母亲郭香兰:同样碌碌无为,比较窝囊,不爱干家务"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djvbxo7b2co0","created":1783731189878,"text":"废土世界","expandState":"expand","layout":null,"font-size":24,"color":"#ffc000"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djvmk998fxs0","created":1783761170818,"text":"世界信息","layout":null,"font-size":16,"font-weight":"bold"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djvmmssjgeg0","created":1783761370072,"text":"世界信息","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvmn9gzfog0","created":1783761406379,"text":"政府结构","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvmnn2i4rc0","created":1783761435978,"text":"针对超能力者态度","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djvmi8wc7lk0","created":1783761013309,"text":"李其乐","layout":null,"font-weight":"bold","font-size":16,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djvml701ryo0","created":1783761244273,"text":"家庭信息","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvmlx13pvc0","created":1783761300933,"text":"身份背景","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvmme9ws3k0","created":1783761338472,"text":"行为与性格","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]}]},"template":"right","theme":"wire","version":"1.4.43"}